    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1955-05-20T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1955-05-20T10:00:00-05:00" n="101"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d101">
                <head>101. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Embassy in Egypt</gloss> to the
                        <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d101fn1">Source: Department of State, Central
                        Files, 684A.86/5–2055. Top Secret; Alpha; Limit Distribution;<gloss
                            target="#t_Noforn1">Noforn</gloss>. Received at 11:56 p.m. Repeated to
                        London.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="italic">Cairo</hi>
                        </placeName>,<date calendar="gregorian" when="1955-05-20T17:00:00+02:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1955—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1750. In view <persName corresp="#p_NNNGA1">Nasser</persName>’s reaction
                        <persName corresp="#p_SA1">Stevenson</persName> approach regarding high
                    level talks with Israelis (<gloss target="#t_mytel1">mytel</gloss> 1749<note
                        n="2" xml:id="d101fn2">See <ref target="#d99fn3">footnote 3, Document
                            99</ref>.</note>) broader matters regarding Israel did not arise.
                    However I understand <persName corresp="#p_SA1">Stevenson</persName> message to
                        <gloss target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss> states very specifically his view
                    Alpha clearly impossible for time being. While I fear (and Embassy staff feels
                    certain) this most probably the case, it my present intention have another try
                    in few days.</p>
                <p>It interesting <persName corresp="#p_NNNGA1">Nasser</persName> accused members
                    British Embassy spreading rumors against him of late in much same manner he
                    spoke to me regarding activities of Americans. He also showed resentment that
                        <persName corresp="#p_SA1">Stevenson</persName> “had taken the lead” in
                    keeping Western diplomats away from airport upon his return.<note n="3"
                        xml:id="d101fn3">Reference is to <persName corresp="#p_NNNGA1"
                            >Nasser</persName>’s return from the Afro-Asian Conference at
                        Bandung.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BHA1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Byroade</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
